			<div class="row-fluid">
				<div class="span12 text-center">
					<h1 class="muted">Post on my fridge</h1>
  					<h4 class="muted">Just sticky notes on virtual fridges.</h4>
					<div class="span12">
						<form class="form-inline">
							<div class="btn-group">
							    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-large" {{action "toDemo"}} >
									<i class="icon-white icon-signin"></i> Try it now
								</button>
							</div>
						</form>		  	      
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row-fluid">
				<div class="span10 offset1">
					<div class="thumbnail">
						<img src="../../images/demo.jpeg" alt="">
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row-fluid">
		<div class="span10 offset1">
			<div class="alert">
			 	<h4>Warning <i class="icon-exclamation-sign"></i></h4>
			 	The application is still under heavy development, the data are likely to be lost, have fun!
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row-fluid">
		<div class="span10 offset1">
			<div class="span6 well">
				<h3>Freedom <i class="icon-user"></i></h3>
				<p>
					Tired of authentication and access management? There is nothing like this here, everyone can add or delete content.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="span6 well">
				<h3>Easy <i class="icon-heart"></i></h3>
				<p>
					To access or create a fridge use the search box or type directly the fridge name in the url /fridge/<em>fridge name</em>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row-fluid">
		<div class="span10 offset1">
			<div class="span6 well">
				<h3>Share <i class="icon-share"></i></h3>
				<p>
					You can share content on a fridge in real time with your friends while chatting.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="span6 well">
				<h3>Multimedia <i class="icon-film"></i></h3>
				<p>
					To share a video (youtube/vimeo/dailymotion) or a picture, just insert the url in the content.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
